column2: Gillette Psycho Razor with Key Prison Institution Mental Hospital NOS
column3: I am sell one   Gillette Psycho Razor with replica aluminum key for 100     nbsp     The underside of the head is stamped the Gillette logo Y 4 MARCA REGIST and IND BRASILEIRA This is a Y 4 Razor manufactured in the fourth quarter of 1978 nbspMade in Brazil     nbsp   The razor is new old stock and has never been used This razor comes with an aluminum replica key When I hadnbspthe keys made I had them use stainless steel for the hex head inserts for durability So the part that tightens and loosens the razor is stainless steel     nbsp    Check out my photos for more detail       nbsp  These were made for Prisons and Psychiatric hospitals The razor requires a special key at the bottom of the razor which the guard or orderly carried The key is inserted into the handle and unscrews the head so a razor blade can be changed then the key is used to screw the head back in place and the razor was then given to the prisoners or psychiatric patients since they couldnt get the blade out without the key These came in boxes of 10 razors with one key nbsp This auction is for ONE razor with key This rare razor is a very unique part of the history of shaving implements that are no longer made These use the modern double edge blades and are great shavers and also great to display as conversation pieces due to their rarity and the specific population for which they were made    nbsp  This razor come from the old Allegheny County Jail in Pittsburgh PA which was opened in 1886 and closed in 1995 The jail was designed by world renowned architect Henry Hobson Richardson and is on the National Register of Historic Places This razor are quite rare dont pass up this opportunity for a great vintage prison and safety razor   nbsp  I also have stainless steel keys available for an up charge If you would prefer the stainless steel key instead of the aluminum key the cost is an additional 600    As far as a weight comparison for the different keys Original Key  153 oz Stainless Steel Key  125 oz Aluminum Key  49 oz   nbsp  I am also selling the keys separately  Stainless Steel Key 32  Aluminum Key 26            nbsp      Check out my photos for more detail     nbsp you Mapquest Bullittsville KY I am about a mile or so from that location

column2: Firewood Green or Kiln Dried The Good Stuff
column3: This is The Good Stuff  We have plenty of wood in stock and is ready for immediate delivery all year long  We are an approved supplier  Vt Fuel Assistance Program  Delivery is available to most any location for a reasonable fee  Our kiln dried firewood has been certified by Vermont State Dept of Agriculture for proper heat treatment This provides for thorough drying and also  eliminates any insects that you might find in seasoned wood It also helps deter re infestation of insects in your wood pile  This certification enables us to legally transport our kiln dried firewood to areas that are quarantined for invasive species such as the Asian Longhorn Beetle and the Emerald Ash Borer  We have many cords available to cut split and dry  for your needs This is mostly Hard maple Beech White Ash and Soft  Maple with some Red Oak and Yellow Birch There is occasionally a log  of some other hardwood species mixed in  Our Kiln dried firewood is available in the 16  length and sells cut and split ready to burn This is  all quality hardwood dried to a maximum of 25 percent moisture  content inside most pieces 15 to 20 percent Our kilns are heated to  between 180 and 200 deg F this process eliminates bugs mold and fungus  Green firewood is available in 16 and 22 lengths cut and split  other lengths are available to meet your needs   We offer outdoor boiler wood which is green wood that is made from  smaller logs mostly in the 6 to 12 diameter range It is cut 22  long and is NOT split  If you have special wood requirements let us know and we will try to accommodate your specific needs  Please call 802 4534884 for more information 700 AM to 430 PM  Monday through Friday  Weekend delivery is available
